text: Whoopee! is a 1930 American musical comedy movie directed by Thornton Freeland and starring Eddie Cantor, Ethel Shutta, Paul Gregory, Eleanor Hunt, Jack Rutherford, Walter Law, Spencer Charters. It was distributed by United Artists. The movie was nominated for Best Art Direction in 1931. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * * * Category:1930 comedy movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Thornton Freeland
